metadata.name: Winter Twilight - The Bridge
metadata.description: Palatial Frostscapes is about the stillness of winter, the muffled sounds of snow-covered landscapes, and the warm and welcoming light of fireplaces. Snow airbrushes the mess of late autumn, accentuates the magnificent proportions of architectural marvels, and shifts us into a parallel dimension. Frosty twilight is more eery than spring sunsets, and winter sunshine is more crisp than desert sunrises. This is what creates the magic we feel as we step into the Frostscapes.
